He came to us because of prostrate problems...

88
00:05:54,220 --> 00:05:56,930
某种社会影响性的问题无法解决
and some sort of social infection that doesn't go away.

89
00:05:57,730 --> 00:06:01,480
外加 我认为他是屁股中弹 但我无法确认这件事
Plus, I think he got shot in the ass, but I can't confirm that.

90
00:06:01,650 --> 00:06:04,230
总之 你最好不要去惹他
Anyway, he's the man that you don't want to aggravate.

91
00:06:04,400 --> 00:06:05,860
你一向这么快乐吗
Are you always this happy?

92
00:06:06,030 --> 00:06:07,570
- 康纳  - 长官
- Cronauer.  - Sir.

93
00:06:08,740 --> 00:06:10,320
