How you doing? You could fly to Guam with those.

104
00:06:46,940 --> 00:06:49,690
飞行员康纳 长官
Airman Cronauer, sir.

105
00:06:49,860 --> 00:06:53,280
知道吗 偶而向我敬个礼不会害死你们的
You know, it wouldn't kill you people to salute me once in a while.

106
00:06:53,450 --> 00:06:56,080
- 抱歉  - 谢谢
- Sorry.  - Thanks.

107
00:06:56,870 --> 00:06:58,700
