I understand you're pretty funny as a deejay.

108
00:06:58,870 --> 00:07:02,080
是的 嗯 说笑话是我的一种喜好
And, well, comedy is a kind of hobby of mine.

109
00:07:02,250 --> 00:07:05,420
嗯 事实上 那不仅是一种喜好
Well, actually, it's a little more than just a hobby.

110
